Name: Battle Imagine - Jungle Goblin Warrior
Description:
Use to activate or upgrade Jungle Goblin Warrior's Battle Imagine skill: Stunt! Commanding Roar.

Stunt! Commanding Roar
Summon Elite: Jungle Goblin Warrior and roars.
Upon the skill cast, your Strength is increased for a period, and during the duration, your next hit deals additional Attack Damage to the first target.
